Description:Test puzzle for replaying a persist loop with a repeated library-choice prompt: Kitchen Finks plus Vizier of Remedies plus Viscera Seer and Zulaport Cutthroat. Record one cycle that sacrifices Kitchen Finks to Viscera Seer, handles the Scry 1 choice, lets persist return Kitchen Finks without a -1/-1 counter, and lets the drain and life-gain triggers resolve. Repeat until the opponent is defeated.

